inlineContent.text: These constants are relevant only in macOS, and not in iOS.
Audio unit parameter flags, for use in the
data structure , serve as a dictionary-like set of information about an audio unit parameter. Parameter flag bit position 19 is reserved.

abstract.text: Record or play audio, convert formats, parse audio streams, and configure your audio session.
